1.0.0 2018-04-14
================
Breaking changes for those using ssh::install and ssh::config classes individually:
  * These classes were removed
  * Module simplified and functionality moved to ssh class
  * Hiera keynames changed due to above

Testing:
  * Update to latest PDQTest
  * Update acceptance tests to check SSH service operational
  * Extra test for manual installation (AIX/Solaris)
  * Removed and regenerated the rspec tests for simplicity

Documentation:
  * ...There is documentation now ;-)
